FrankenTui.Net Repository License Notice

This repository contains both original FrankenTui.Net material and material
derived from FrankenTUI. The applicable license depends on the provenance of the
material.

1. FrankenTUI-derived material

Any material in this repository that is copied from, translated from, ported
from, adapted from, or otherwise derived from FrankenTUI is distributed under
the FrankenTUI upstream license reproduced in
LICENSES/FrankenTUI-UPSTREAM.txt.

Copyright in that upstream-derived material remains with Jeffrey Emanuel and any
other upstream rights holders, if any. The FrankenTUI OpenAI/Anthropic rider
remains in force for all such material.

2. Original FrankenTui.Net material

Repository materials authored originally for FrankenTui.Net and not derived
from FrankenTUI are Copyright (c) 2026 FrankenTui.Net contributors and are
licensed under the MIT License reproduced in LICENSES/MIT.txt.

3. Mixed files and combined works

If a file or deliverable combines original FrankenTui.Net material with
FrankenTUI-derived material, treat it as containing FrankenTUI-derived material
and comply with the FrankenTUI upstream license for that portion. Nothing in
this repository grants broader rights in FrankenTUI-derived material than the
upstream license grants.

4. Project framing

FrankenTui.Net is presented as a faithful .NET port and translation of
FrankenTUI into another implementation medium, not as a clean-room
reimplementation. See PROVENANCE.md and CHARTER.md for the governing project
framing.
